Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:41.64,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Furom, iestrov...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:43.14,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Elmuto... Eril!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:46.23,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Natow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:48.02,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,顯現吧【暴風】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:51.77,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:53.90,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,顯現吧 緊繃的大氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:55.11,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,【迷途者】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:56.57,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,【老紳士】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:09.50,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,這就完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:11.05,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,投降嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.70,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,投降 不！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:13.84,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:21.91,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:23.18,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.23,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:27.69,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Ilm, es, alas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:45.04,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Schu, limic...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.69,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,顯現吧 爆破消散之物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:49.17,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,【破壞者】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:01.79,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,這沒完沒了的 不愧是亂破師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.11,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:12.27,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,還有什麼小伎倆可用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:15.42,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我還能打
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:16.07,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.80,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,昨天說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:21.78,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,魔法師的強弱 由經驗決定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.10,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,你缺的是閱歷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:27.58,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Blow away! The Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:33.50,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:53.19,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,Assa, schron, misam, winhel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.82,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,顯現吧【阻御者】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.20,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.86,Default,David,0,0,0,,到此為止了 英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.19,Default,Red,0,0,0,,遺體 交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.54,Default,David,0,0,0,,怎麼了 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:24.47,Default,David,0,0,0,,第一次拿到遺體該高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.96,Default,David,0,0,0,,倒是笑一笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.95,Default,Red,0,0,0,,喜悅 並不覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:29.77,Default,David,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:34.52,Default,David,0,0,0,,話說回來 還真有點嚇人啊…這玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:35.37,Default,Red,0,0,0,,無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,父親的遺體 神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:39.10,Default,David,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:43.87,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,真希望 往後都能像這樣趕在白丫頭之前找到英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.66,Default,David,0,0,0,,嗯 保持這勢頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:49.95,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.46,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不論精神還是肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.69,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,一旦被僱傭便不會背叛僱主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:58.46,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,這是我們唯一的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:07.11,Default,David,0,0,0,,怎麼了 莫非是想起那個亂破師小子了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.21,0:05:08.85,Default,Red,0,0,0,,否定 堅決否定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:10.44,Default,David,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:11.44,Default,David,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:14.12,Default,David,0,0,0,,很危險啊 我可在駕馬車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:16.15,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,誰讓你說話不經大腦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.07,Default,Red,0,0,0,,遺體 收集的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:25.22,Default,Red,0,0,0,,白色的冒牌女兒 父親 憑悼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.57,Default,Red,0,0,0,,目的 實在明確
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.42,Default,Red,0,0,0,,相對 我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,復仇 模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:35.96,Default,Red,0,0,0,,具體內容 難以掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.27,Default,Selma,0,0,0,,這估計…集齊後就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.38,Default,David,0,0,0,,嗯 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以咱就盡可能多地收集這玩意…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.67,Default,Red,0,0,0,,無禮！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:47.97,Default,David,0,0,0,,知道啦 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:51.69,Default,David,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.14,Default,Red,0,0,0,,奇伊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:58.65,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,拿到了嗎 賈茲皇帝的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:00.78,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.36,Default,David,0,0,0,,又突然冒出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:09.58,Default,David,0,0,0,,我們正好想趕超那個白色丫頭和亂破師兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:11.00,Default,David,0,0,0,,下個遺體在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:13.30,Default,David,0,0,0,,你是帶情報來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.46,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,嗯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.87,Default,Red,0,0,0,,地點 說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:19.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,從這裏朝海岸方向走一天有個漁村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:22.40,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,叫克裏·摩根的英雄在那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.92,Default,Red,0,0,0,,抓緊前往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.85,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,不用這麼急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:27.76,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,我還有個情報
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.35,Default,Red,0,0,0,,說！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:32.22,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,遠海的小島 不妨一去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:33.85,Default,Red,0,0,0,,島？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.24,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,沒準會遇到好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:44.30,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,基列特隊長的遺物 繼續保持在這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.49,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,我希望隊長回來隨時都能用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:51.04,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,所以 隊名也保持基列特隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.69,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,嗯 我聽機關長說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:57.17,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.26,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,這樣下去沒法反擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:10.86,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,陷阱的狀況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.22,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,幾乎全被拆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.42,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:16.18,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托魯 阿卡莉 投降 否定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.60,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.44,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,完全無法近身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.61,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,慢人一手只能被動挨打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:24.82,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我去當誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.46,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,誘餌 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:29.11,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,躲在這也只會跟石頭一起被炸飛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.37,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不成功便成仁 只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.47,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,懂了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:38.27,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我盡量分散她的注意 阿卡莉從反方向進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:42.52,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡別急 先找個能保證射擊的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.15,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,成功率第一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.46,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,好 行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:50.44,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,吾即為鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:53.69,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,吾鋼故無畏 吾鋼故無惑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:57.23,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,若敵當前 便捨棄一切顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.34,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,吾乃滅敵之兇器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.79,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,鐵血轉化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.45,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,想抄我後路？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:14.99,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Alay, salama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.54,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,沒錯嘉依卡 就這樣繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.67,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Sabah, amasala, missah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:27.71,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,護盾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:36.85,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:37.68,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.08,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.99,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Salimic, binnu, alay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.02,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,顯現吧 衝擊粉碎之物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.46,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,【重擊者】
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.10,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.48,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.98,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,吾乃凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.88,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托魯 沒問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.98,0:09:36.36,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:37.61,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.43,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:42.33,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 勝過一招 已經確保
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.85,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,是啊 贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.01,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,想做還是能做到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:57.15,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,是我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:00.04,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.67,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,不只是因為那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:04.39,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,沒發覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:08.95,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,剛剛你想全力保護他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:14.03,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,魔法攻擊的威力 關鍵就看魔法師的思緒有多強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.51,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:24.37,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,果然你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.63,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,看你就是皇帝的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,理解 感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.15,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.55,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,啊啦 它是你養的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.01,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:47.83,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,珂羅蒂雅女士 到約定的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不懂風情 我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:54.79,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,是 但非常抱歉 請盡快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.15,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,工作堆積很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:59.12,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,總之先喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.10,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,這點時間沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.18,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,期待 喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:05.01,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,想吃各種葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:24.18,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,【深夜中拔出的劍 無法再收回鞘中】
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:27.02,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,聽不太懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.33,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:31.86,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,不過簽上所說 我會謹記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:34.78,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,薇薇的寫了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:35.57,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,我的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:40.22,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,【想拯救所愛之人 要用你不變的愛】
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:45.46,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,薇薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.89,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,是基列特隊長的筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.63,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,在【四月號】裏找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:59.41,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,剛才 我跟尼克拉隊長確認了內容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:04.68,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,與嘉依卡和賈茲皇帝相關的疑問及考察 記得密密麻麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:10.95,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,隊長有多麼關心嘉依卡一案 全都體現在這筆記上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:18.25,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,這裏 主要保管者從賈茲帝國城押收的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:22.03,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,其實 我也沒詳細調查過這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:25.94,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,正如筆記中所寫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:31.00,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,他那樣的魔法師 沒留下任何魔法技術資料 實在不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:35.10,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,於是 我重新查閱了這裏的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.96,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,找到了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.93,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,賈茲皇帝討伐隊的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:45.80,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,遺產？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.56,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,卡蓮小姐 這個可以交給我保管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:52.00,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你看就是為了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:58.65,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,我會繼續調查這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:02.36,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,希望你像往常一樣 繼續追捕嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.83,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,是 我做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.48,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,康拉德機關長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.18,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,什麼事 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.88,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,我跟薇薇聊過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.11,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:43.96,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,戰爭結束多年 居然還會這樣痛失部下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:44.69,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:49.91,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,亞伯力克的見解或許該多重視下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:50.85,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.29,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,那麼 薇薇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:55.18,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,是 她很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.41,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,另外 機關長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.72,Default,Curren,0,0,0,,最近 煙抽的有點多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.65,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,一點粗陋之物 還請嘗嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:21.61,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,葡萄 格外甜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:24.28,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,新鮮葡萄 全部絕品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:26.42,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,把那個拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.24,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:34.01,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,這是說好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.63,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,父親的遺體？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:36.79,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.02,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你沒用過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:40.18,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,遺體嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:40.67,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:45.50,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,戰後五年間就建了這麼大的葡萄園和酒窖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:49.14,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,還以為肯定把皇帝遺體當思念料用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:53.78,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,嘛 這我也不是沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:57.10,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,用它做葡萄酒味道肯定有保證
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.33,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,但是 總有點牴觸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:04.99,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你…跟我們之前遇到的英雄不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:06.77,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:11.51,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,嘛 討伐隊成員中 怪癖的人本來就多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:15.25,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,戰爭一結束 有很多人流落街頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:20.31,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,我不想變成那樣 所以有了人生目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:24.95,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,而且 雖然作為英雄拿了遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:26.07,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,但那不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:31.39,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,聽說叫嘉依卡的女孩在收集遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:35.11,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,就絕對【如果看著順眼就送給她】
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:38.81,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,遺體放在我這 畢竟不如放在女兒那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:40.77,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:42.71,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,對了 你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,知道遺產的所在了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:45.88,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,遺產？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,遺產 存在？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.53,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,啊啦 你不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:53.59,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,賈茲城陷落時 魔法師殘黨說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:55.94,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,皇帝有份遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.88,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,求你們 請你饒我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.84,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,我用情報作交換
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.55,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:15.44,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,我知道賈茲皇帝的重要機密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:16.34,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:22.06,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,接到賈茲皇帝旨意的魔法師 不久前調去了國外的孤島
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:26.15,Default,Wizard,0,0,0,,那裏藏有皇帝的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:31.16,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,謝謝你的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:38.08,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,但是我們 奉命殲滅賈茲城內所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:41.78,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,即便是一隻老鼠 也不可放過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:50.68,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,討伐隊的記錄人員 將秘密和皇帝遺產一事 都上報了聯合軍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.25,0:16:55.22,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,皇帝的遺產 如今何處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:59.23,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,雖然聯合軍著手調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:02.34,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,結果什麼都沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:03.82,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,什麼都？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.44,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,然後調查就被腰斬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.56,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,破城後把城內翻了個遍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:14.41,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,但魔法技術相關的實驗道具和資料 一件都沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:21.69,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,大推測 賈茲皇帝派出的魔法師 把這些東西都帶上了孤島
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:25.46,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,島 父親的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:28.63,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,不過遺體能還給你就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:29.90,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.88,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,還要繼續旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:32.76,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:36.88,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,那…可能有遺體的地方 我給你寫出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:37.91,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你知道在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:38.53,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,其餘英雄的名字和出身地罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:45.27,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,還剩這麼多 別客氣快點吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.50,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,我只記得大概 而且都過了五年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:50.64,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,不知如今還在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:54.29,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,這樣一來 進度能加快不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:58.07,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯 可以跟撞大運的旅行說拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.81,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,是吧 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.59,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:11.84,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,都大半夜了還啟程 再住一晚多好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:14.34,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,畢竟是我們來打攪的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.97,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,至少喝杯葡萄酒再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:18.91,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我對酒沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.59,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,葡萄酒能滋潤人生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.40,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,這是酒鬼的說辭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:26.81,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,等你懂了這說辭 記得回來很找我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.40,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,等我懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.86,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,承蒙照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.71,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,禮物 大量 感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:34.70,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,珂羅蒂雅的葡萄 絕品 不可能忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:36.07,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.94,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,交給那個不知真假的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:50.20,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,對您而言明明是勳章
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.88,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,那不是什麼勳章
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只是個擺設
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:58.57,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,現在我眼中的勳章…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是今年的葡萄酒 能賣個更好價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.55,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:41.31,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,怎麼了 做惡夢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:45.97,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,凄慘的記憶 斬首的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:49.26,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,但是那個記憶 假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是真的 我已經死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:55.04,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我自己 冒牌的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:58.14,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,在那之前 我 什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:02.17,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嘉依卡 複數存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:05.20,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,皇帝真正的女兒 有傳言已死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:08.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我的記憶 混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:10.20,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,胸中不安 心煩意亂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:15.76,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,確實 你會這樣想也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.34,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,但是 這不影響你的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:24.70,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,目的 遺體收集 父親 憑悼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:28.13,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,所以 只能向著它前進啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:33.08,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我和阿卡莉 都一心要為主人你達成目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:34.72,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,這不就夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:37.25,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,沒錯 我也這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:44.53,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,天也亮了 咱們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:47.38,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:54.34,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你 是八英雄之一 葛倫·冬克沃特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.04,0:20:56.86,Default,Glen,0,0,0,,嘛 是沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.38,Default,Glen,0,0,0,,你們 身手不簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:04.54,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,把皇帝的遺體交出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:08.24,Default,Glen,0,0,0,,這個嘛…遺體已經不在我這了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:08.98,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:12.73,Default,Glen,0,0,0,,昨天 交給一個紅色丫頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:13.94,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,紅色？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:16.24,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,紅嘉依卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.33,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嘉依卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.91,0:21:24.60,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,他他們也還在收集遺體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:26.85,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,離我們應該不遠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:33.16,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,剩下就是亞蘭·托拉蒙塔納子爵 史蒂芬·哈爾特根 科林·摩根嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:36.15,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,可別被紅嘉依卡搶了先
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:37.96,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,嘉依卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:42.97,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,父親的島 尋找 希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:48.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,找到它 我 什麼人 理解可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:49.33,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:51.69,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:54.45,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,解明疑惑 請求
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:30.83,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,居住港口城市的英雄 魁梧的槍兵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:33.13,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,工頭 很強 困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.23,0:23:35.08,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 海上故事 希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:37.39,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,但是 在此之前 戰鬥不可避免
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:39.83,Title,Chaika,0,0,0,,下集 若夢迷心之港
